Others: The Gambia National Team has a 2-0 head-to-head record against Tunisia.
Their last encounter was during the 2022 AFCON group stages in Cameroon, where Gambia won 1-0.
The upcoming match is a crucial Africa Cup of Nations (AFCON) qualifier.
Tunisia seeks revenge while Gambia aims to extend their winning streak and secure a spot in the AFCON 2024 finals.
